author: matzew
msg: Fixed a logic error in SimpleSelectOneRenderer.getSubmittedValue() where the
submitted value was set to "" if it was null, which is not valid for
selectOne* when valuePassThru is false.  Added a check for valuePassThru and
if it's false, submitted value is left as null.
